CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, pg. 17 reads: "...6. Miss Ida Mae Mauney, H.J. Heinz Company hostess, poses with Raymond A. Malsch, Heinz representative, in their picturesque booth...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Ida Mae Mauney and Raymond A. Malsch posed in Heinz booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
